OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FApart from the odd shower it
OL,6,Fwill be dry today. Often cloudy across
OL,7,Fthe south and west, but some bright
OL,8,Fspells breaking through along the
OL,9,Fcoasts. Brisk southerly winds along
OL,10,Fthe east coast. Mild inland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,13,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,14,Fdry with clear periods across the
OL,15,Fnorth and east. Brisk winds along the
OL,16,Feast coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FMainly dry and cloudy,
OL,19,Fchance of some occasional brightness.
OL,20,FPatchy rain likely to spread east
OL,21,Flater in the day. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
