OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright spells and a few showers on
OL,7,FThursday, but some dry spells of
OL,8,Fweather too. Chance of early rain on
OL,9,FFriday, otherwise mainly dry. Dry for
OL,10,Fmost Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
